name: .UED File Extension
summary: Learn about .UED files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can import UED data sets into ClimGen (Windows) and CropSyst (Windows). You can also view and edit the data set a UED contains using the UED Weather editor, which is included with the ClimGen and CropSyst programs.
